Sada ste na sigurnom.

55
00:13:45,639 --> 00:13:46,401
Usli ste u zabranjenu zonu.

56
00:14:24,502 --> 00:14:25,855
Pazi, Dzoi, kuda ides.

57
00:14:29,340 --> 00:14:31,581
Mama, mogu li sladoled?
Naravno, kakav zelis?

58
00:15:43,117 --> 00:15:45,790
Od cega je ovaj?
Pistaci i vanila.

59
00:15:47,120 --> 00:15:51,318
Sta imamo ovde?
Lepe, privlacne...

60
00:15:52,208 --> 00:15:53,880
Gladiuse.

61
00:15:56,779 --> 00:15:59,373
Kontrolisi se malo.

62
00:16:02,252 --> 00:16:02,775
Zasto uvek u ovim stvarima?

63
00:16:09,030 --> 00:16:09,837
Sta je ovo?

64
00:16:11,951 --> 00:16:13,304
Idem za njima.

65
